snippet: Jets quarterback Mark Sanchez has received tepid endorsements from Coach Rex Ryan and the owner Woody Johnson.
abstract: New York Jets quarterback Mark Sanchez says he is not worried about losing his starting position, after receiving tepid endorsements from coach Rex Ryan and owner Woody Johnson.
